data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath McKinleyville home. Low maintenance and well-maintained situated on a south-facing, sunny corner lot with an inviting covered front porch. You'll love the open floor plan with a spacious kitchen featuring plenty of storage and upgraded stainless steel appliances. Lovely laminate floors throughout the downstairs. The upstairs is bright and cheery, with plenty of windows to let the light in and pretty easterly views of the hills. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bath and dual closets. Enjoy BBQs on the patio in the fully fenced backyard - just waiting for your creative touches. Nicely finished garage. Cement siding. Sprinklers front and back. Great location close to everything, including schools and shopping.  Just minutes from Cal Poly Humboldt and the ocean. Great condition, suitable for all types of financing including FHA and VA.  A nice home for a great price! Call your favorite agent to schedule a private showing.
